### Test Pronoun Resolution Feature
### Phase 1: Create conversation and ask first question

# Step 1: Login
POST https://localhost:7189/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "admin",
  "password": "Admin@123"
}

### Save token from response above, then use in next requests
@token = YOUR_TOKEN_HERE
@connectionId = YOUR_CONNECTION_ID_HERE

###
# Step 2: Get connections
GET https://localhost:7189/api/connections
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###
# Step 3: Create new conversation
POST https://localhost:7189/api/conversations
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Test Pronoun Resolution",
  "connectionId": "{{connectionId}}"
}

### Save conversationId from response
@conversationId = YOUR_CONVERSATION_ID_HERE

###
# Step 4: First question - "Show me all products"
POST https://localhost:7189/api/v2/agent/process
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "connectionId": "{{connectionId}}",
  "question": "Show me all products",
  "conversationId": "{{conversationId}}"
}

### Expected: Should return products list with SQL query
### Check logs for:
### - [EnhancedAgent] 📦 Extracted context from history
### - Primary entity: Products

###
# Step 5: Follow-up question with pronoun - "How many of them are in stock?"
POST https://localhost:7189/api/v2/agent/process
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "connectionId": "{{connectionId}}",
  "question": "How many of them are in stock?",
  "conversationId": "{{conversationId}}"
}

### Expected behavior:
### ✅ Should detect pronoun "them"
### ✅ Should rewrite to "How many Products are in stock?"
### ✅ Should NOT ask for clarification
### ✅ Should reach 12 processing steps (not just 1)
### ✅ Response should include:
###    - contextEntities: ["Products"]
###    - primaryEntity: "Products"
###    - pronounsResolved: true
###
### Check logs for:
### [ConversationManager] 🔍 Detected pronouns: [them]
### [CoreferenceResolver] ✏️ Rewritten: 'How many of them...' → 'How many Products...'
### [EnhancedAgent] 📦 Context entities: [Products], Primary: Products
### [EnhancedAgent] 🔄 Question enriched

###
# Step 6: Vietnamese test - "Có bao nhiêu cái đang còn hàng?"
POST https://localhost:7189/api/v2/agent/process
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "connectionId": "{{connectionId}}",
  "question": "Có bao nhiêu cái đang còn hàng?",
  "conversationId": "{{conversationId}}"
}

### Expected:
### ✅ Should detect Vietnamese pronoun "cái"
### ✅ Should rewrite to include "Products"
### ✅ Should work without clarification

###
# Step 7: Test with "those"
POST https://localhost:7189/api/v2/agent/process
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "connectionId": "{{connectionId}}",
  "question": "Show me those with price > 100",
  "conversationId": "{{conversationId}}"
}

### Expected:
### ✅ Should detect pronoun "those"
### ✅ Should rewrite to "Show me Products with price > 100"

###
# Step 8: Get conversation messages to verify context
GET https://localhost:7189/api/conversations/{{conversationId}}/messages
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Expected:
### ✅ Should show all messages with structured context
### ✅ Each assistant message should have:
###    - sqlQuery
###    - targetTable (extracted)
###    - entitiesReferenced (from SQL parser)
###    - primaryEntity
